WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.500
A tube-map-style diagram is attached to the wall, 
covered with post-its and scribbles.

00:01.500 --> 00:03.500
The camera pans across the board.

00:03.500 --> 00:05.000
Tube lines represent organisational silos. 

00:05.000 --> 00:06.000
Stations represent process stages.

00:06.000 --> 00:06.500
The tool allowed employees to share feedback, 
helping shape new processes around their needs.
